/ technical education in 163 best institutions which includes \u2013 23 IIT, 19 IIM, 29 NIT, 17 Law Universities.Ph.D Level \u2013  All candidates who have completed their PG Course and are pursuing Ph.D will get Rs. 15000 per month for the upcoming 3 years for research purpose.Research Work \u2013 If the research subject is accepted by top 100 universities than students will get Rs. 1 lakh.However, only the students who are not paying IT returns can apply for Chief Minister Fellowship Yojana.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}